<section class="container">
    <div class="row text-start">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h3 id="heading">YelpCampGlobal.com</h3>
                <hr>
                <p>
                    YelpCampGlobal is a project that I made in my Web Development Bootcamp. It functions
                    as a Yelp like application but for campgrounds. This site was more of a trial 
                    run for me to code along and play with the different tools and technolgies that were used. 
                </p>
                <p>
                <strong>Functionality:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Create an account, sign in, sign out</li>
                    <li>Create a campground with a title, name, description, and price</li>
                    <li>Edit or delete that campground as long as your account was the one that created it</li>
                    <li>Comment on other campgrounds</li>
                    <li>Edit or delete those comments as long as you your account was the one that created them</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
                <p>
                <strong>Stack/Tools:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Express.js (NodeJS)</li>
                    <li>Passport.js (Authentication)</li>
                    <li>Mongoose (MongoDB)</li>
                    <li>EJS (Embedded JavaScript)</li>
                    <li>HTML</li>
                    <li>CSS</li>
                    <li>Boostrap 4 (Responsive on all device sizes)</li>
                    <li>Flash Messages</li>
                    <li>RESTful Routing</li>
                    <li>Git & Github (Version Control)</li>
                    <li>Font Awesome (icons)</li>
                    <li>Google Fonts</li>
                    <li>Heroku (Deployment)</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
    </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
            <img id="splash" class="portfolioImg" src="https://i.ibb.co/kKf1kJV/Screen-Shot-2019-03-21-at-3-06-00-PM.png">
            <img id="index" class="portfolioImg" src="https://i.ibb.co/yBgRh0W/Screen-Shot-2019-03-21-at-3-28-53-PM.png">
